\b\fs48 \cf0 Installation: Famous 5-minute install\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720
\ls1\ilvl0
\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}Unzip the package in an empty directory and upload everything.\
{\listtext	2.	}Open {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "file:///Users/lloyds/Site-test/wp-admin/install.php"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 wp-admin/install.php}} in your browser. It will take you through the process to set up a 
\f1 wp-config.php
\f0  file with your database connection details.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}If for some reason this doesn't work, don't worry. It doesn't work on all web hosts. Open up 
\f1 wp-config-sample.php
\f0  with a text editor like WordPad or similar and fill in your database connection details.\
{\listtext	2.	}Save the file as 
\f1 wp-config.php
\f0  and upload it.\
{\listtext	3.	}Open {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "file:///Users/lloyds/Site-test/wp-admin/install.php"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 wp-admin/install.php}} in your browser.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	3.	}Once the configuration file is set up, the installer will set up the tables needed for your blog. If there is an error, double check your 
\f1 wp-config.php
\f0  file, and try again. If it fails again, please go to the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wordpress.org/support/"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 support forums}} with as much data as you can gather.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720
\ls1\ilvl0
\b \cf0 {\listtext	4.	}If you did not enter a password, note the password given to you.
\b0  If you did not provide a username, it will be 
\f1 admin
\f0 .\
{\listtext	5.	}The installer should then send you to the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "file:///Users/lloyds/Site-test/wp-login.php"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 login page}}. Sign in with the username and password you chose during the installation. If a password was generated for you, you can then click on 'Profile' to change the password.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320

